{"ID":"20260609131223-ivmhlmg","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609131223-ivmhlmg","title":"2021年新高考Ⅱ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609131235-se3hwjy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131235-se3hwjy","updated":"20260609131235"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"吃喝当然是人生一大乐事，如果生活在太空，我们还能愉快地享用大餐吗？"}]},{"ID":"20260609131235-fy47ggx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131235-fy47ggx","updated":"20260609131235"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最早的太空餐是让人"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":" "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的“牙膏”：宇航员从管子里面挤出半流体的食物，不需要咀嚼便直接咽下去，没有咀嚼的快感，没有多样的选择，首代宇航员的饮食条件相当艰苦。然而，吃货的生产力"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，很快，（   ）。如今，宇航员们已能在太空中自如地使用各种餐具，与地面用餐相当接近。与此同时，太空食品的种类也丰富起来。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"正因为目前国际空间站中有上百种餐品，使得宇航员可以自由选择自己的用餐计划——然而这一用餐计划是每八天循环一次的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。而且宇航员们还在不停地开发新的太空料理：小饼干、寿司、花生酱冰棍，甚至是“昨的咖啡”——采访中一位航天飞机的指挥官曾自豪地展示过一批再生水，而原料是什么，自然"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131235-xem5lam","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131235-xem5lam","updated":"20260609131235"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然而，制订太空菜谱仍然受到很大的限制。大部分蔬果在宇宙中最多只能保持两天鲜度，空间站中新鲜食品"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":" "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，绝大多数食品只能脱水或加工成罐头运上太空。目前科学家们正想方设法解决这一难题。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131223-sc2knta","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609131223-sc2knta","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-aa4fs9p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-aa4fs9p","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．依次填入文中横线上的词语，全都恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-iue0c9n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-iue0c9n","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．望而却步  不胜枚举  不言而喻  寥寥无几"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-74ei3l0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-74ei3l0","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．踌躇不前  不可低估  心照不宣  寥寥无几"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-qmgm09s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-qmgm09s","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．望而却步  不可低估  不言而喻  极其稀缺"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-6nm8h2p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-6nm8h2p","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．踌躇不前  不胜枚举  心照不宣  极其稀缺"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-avpla05","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-avpla05","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．下列填入文中括号内的语句，衔接最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-97m1ah0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-97m1ah0","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．人们就发明了种种能在无重力环境中使用的餐具，并且还有咖啡杯和煎锅"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-fm9yast","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-fm9yast","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．人们就发明了种种能在无重力环境中使用的餐具，甚至还有咖啡杯和煎锅"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-wdlewpr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-wdlewpr","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．人们就将种种能在无重力环境中使用的餐具发明出来，而且包括咖啡杯和煎锅"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-m1p8iem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-m1p8iem","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．人们就将种种能在无重力环境中使用的餐具发明出来，还包括咖啡杯和煎锅"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-x0h4zzz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-x0h4zzz","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．文中画波浪线的句子有语病，下列修改最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-1zrg1ke","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-1zrg1ke","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．目前国际空间站中有上百种餐品，宇航员可以自由选择自己的用餐计划——虽然这一用餐计划是每八天循环一次的。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-gd904ep","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-gd904ep","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．正因为目前国际空间站中有上百种餐品，使得宇航员可以自由选择自己的用餐计划——虽然这一用餐计划是每八天循环一次的。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-a69zgqg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-a69zgqg","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．正因为目前国际空间站中有上百种餐品，所以宇航员可以自由选择自己的用餐计划——然而这一用餐计划是每八天循环一次的。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131247-gzwsodu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131247-gzwsodu","updated":"20260609131247"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．目前国际空间站中有上百种餐品，这使得宇航员可以自由选择自己的用餐计划——然而这一用餐计划是每八天循环一次的。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131223-rhp4kk4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609131223-rhp4kk4","updated":"20260609131258"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609131257-xjo48eg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131257-xjo48eg","updated":"20260609131258"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．C    19．B    20．A"}]},{"ID":"20260609131223-noicjxz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609131223-noicjxz","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-cbesupz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-cbesupz","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题考查学生正确使用成语的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-z42lbi4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-z42lbi4","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一空，望而却步：形容十分害怕困难和危险。踌躇不前：犹豫不决，不敢前进。语境强调太空餐难吃，应选“望而却步”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-677pexp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-677pexp","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二空，不胜枚举：无法一个一个全举出来，形容同一类的人或事物很多。不可低估：不能小看。语境强调“吃货的生产力”不可小看，应选“不可低估”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-qpypvpv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-qpypvpv","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第三空，不言而喻：指不用说就可以明白。形容道理很浅显。心照不宣：指彼此心里明白，而不公开说出来。前面有“自然”，强调不说就明白，应选“不言而喻”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-8d5rrki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-8d5rrki","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第四空，寥寥无几：形容数量少。非常稀少，没有几个。极其稀缺：极其稀少﹐短缺。此处强调空间站中新鲜食品极少，应填“极其稀缺”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-vwdy1aq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-vwdy1aq","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-d6u9c0x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-d6u9c0x","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查学生语言表达简连贯衔接的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-tyxwp6k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-tyxwp6k","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"语境强调的是人们的创造力，应保持“人们就发明了……”的句子结构，排除CD；"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-ypzwfkp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-ypzwfkp","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“还有咖啡杯和煎锅”与前文形成语意递进，句首应用递进连词，而“并且”表并列，排除A。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-ggwsuzr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-ggwsuzr","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-65knv89","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-65knv89","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．本题考查学生辨析并修改病句的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-z5f1zoz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-z5f1zoz","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"划线句有语病："}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-5gub7zo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-5gub7zo","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一是“正因为……使得”搭配不当，可以删掉“正因为”“使得”，也可以把“使得”改为“所以”，或者删掉“正因为”，在“使得”前加“这”，排除B；"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-ouas85w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-ouas85w","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二是“然而”使用错误，因为后面的句子是转折句的前半句，故改为“虽然”，排除CD。"}]},{"ID":"20260609131309-ur3nihp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609131309-ur3nihp","updated":"20260609131309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选A。"}]}]}